

SuperAgent
==========

SuperAgent is a lightweight HTTP request library that provides an easy-to-use API and supports promises.


Example:

const request = request ('superagent');

request
  .get('https://api.example.com/data')
  .then(response => {
     const data = response.body;
     //process the data
     console.log(data)
  })
  .catch(error => {
    //handle the process
    console.error(error);
  });